data.description: Welcome to your mini farm in the heart of Pike County! This spacious home has four large bedrooms for your family upstairs and plenty of gathering space downstairs. The garage has been sealed for climate control to utilize as a fifth bedroom or unseal and make it a garage again. This home sits on 3.68 acres and is mostly fenced and ready for your four legged friends! The front yard is completely fenced for whatever you choose. There is a barn on the property as well with an asphalt floor for storage or to use for stalls for your horses. This home has a private, quiet lot on a dirt road so you are truly in the county.
